criteria.inclusion_criteria:
1. Aged 15 to 65 years male and female;
2. patients require bone grafting including:
(1) bone defect which need less than 15ml bone grafts;
(2) bone non-union or delayed union;
(3) spinal operation needing 5~60ml bone grafts;
3. Be willing sign the informed consent.

criteria.exclusion_criteria:
1. malignant tumor;
2. myelodysplastic syndrome;
3. infected disease;
4. high dose chemoradiotherapy;
5. blood system disease;
6. operation site with infection or Hemoculture positive recently;
7. Hb＜7g/dl or severe coagulation disorders such as PT>10 seconds and platelet less than 60×10^9/L
8. pregnant woman;
9. patients with decompensated cirrhosis,uremia or severe brain trauma;
10. patient paticipating in other clinial trials in the same time.
